nted%20by%20members%20of%20the%20public%2C%20%26quot%3Bat%20parties%2C%20in%20parks%2C%20in%20restaurants%2C%20and%20on%20public%20transportation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELawyers%20for%20Trump%20and%20Bailey%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.documentcloud.org%2Fdocuments%2F25002731-nyag-v-trump-engoron-recusal-decision-20240725%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERead%20Engoron's%20decision%20here.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrumps-fraud-judge-declines-to-recuse-himself-over-nothingburger-2024-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721937327000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F659ff2db43bb77284b9c30b7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrumps-fraud-judge-declines-to-recuse-himself-over-nothingburger-2024-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Trump's%20lawyers%20had%20said%20Judge%20Arthur%20Engoron%20improperly%20spoke%20about%20the%20case%20outside%20the%20courtroom.%20Engoron%20called%20it%20a%20%26quot%3Bnothingburger.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22litaliano%40insider.com%20(Laura%20Italiano)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrumps-fraud-judge-declines-to-recuse-himself-over-nothingburger-2024-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22OpenAI's%20new%20SearchGPT%20prototype%20is%20a%20declaration%20of%20war%20against%20Google%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22ChaGPT%20shadow%20over%20Google%20search%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66a2b2a3a0fc5856d5978ae3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EiStock%3B%20Google%3B%20Rebecca%20Zisser%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption