ummarized%20answers%20and%20links%20included%20at%20the%20bottom.%20It%20also%20shows%20more%20limited%20results%2C%20unlike%20Google%2C%20which%20has%20pages%20of%20related%20links.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222880%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20screenshot%20of%20search%20results%20from%20OpenAI's%20new%20SearchGPT%20prototype%2C%20which%20is%20in%20the%20testing%20phase.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66a2ade2aab37011780a9fa9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221616%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20screenshot%20of%20search%20results%20from%20OpenAI's%20new%20SearchGPT%20prototype%2C%20which%20is%20in%20the%20testing%20phase.%3Cp%3EOpenAI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20intentional%2C%20according%20to%20the%20company's%20announcement.%20OpenAI%20said%20in%20its%20blog%20post%20that%20%26quot%3Bgetting%20answers%20on%20the%20web%20can%20take%20a%20lot%20of%20effort%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20often%20requires%20multiple%20tries%20to%20%26quot%3Bget%20relevant%20results.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20believe%20that%20by%20enhancing%20the%20conversational%20capabilities%20of%20our%20models%20with%20real-time%20information%20from%20the%20web%2C%20finding%20what%20you're%20looking%20for%20can%20be%20faster%20and%20easier%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20company%20said%20in%20the%20announcement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20also%20follow%20up%20with%20SearchGPT%20results%20with%20clarifying%20questions%2C%20or%20click%20on%20a%20button%20on%20the%20lefthand%20side%20to%20see%20a%20longer%20list%20of%20websites%20related%20to%20the%20query.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20example%20of%20a%20search%20for%20%26quot%3Bmusic%20festivals%20in%20boone%20north%20carolina%20in%20august%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20follow-up%20question%20around%20if%20one%20of%20the%20events%20is%20family%20friendly%20yields%20a%20clear%20answer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222880%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20screenshot%20of%20a%20follow-up%20question%20to%20search%20results%20from%20OpenAI's%20SearchGPT%20prototype.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66a2af06aab37011780aa056%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221618%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20follow-up%20question%20%26quot%3Bis%20the%20jones%20house%20one%20family%20friendly%26quot%3B%20yields%20a%20clear%20answer%20along%20with%20supporting%20links%20in%20OpenAI's%20SearchGPT.%3Cp%3EOpenAI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226c06f210-3a86-403f-b2cf-0155c27bda78%5C%22%3EOpenAI%20has%20Google%20in%20its%20crosshairs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20SearchGPT%2C%20OpenAI%20is%20clearly%20positioning%20itself%20against%20Google's%20Search%20Generative%20Experience%20(SGE)%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fperplexity-raising-new-funding-generative-ai-2024%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20startup%20Perplexity's%3C%2Fa%3E%20search%20feature.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle's%20SGE%20also%20gives%20users%20an%20AI-generated%20summary%20of%20search%20results%2C%20but%20the%20feature%20hasn't%20yet%20been%20rolled%20out%20to%20the%20public%2C%20and%20it's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-uses-ai-search-queries-links-answers-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estill%20being%20tested%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Alphabet%20shares%20were%20down%202%25%20within%20an%20hour%20of%20the%20announcement.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EThe%20search%20feature%20will%20be%20able%20to%20search%20the%20web%20in%20real-time%20and%20automatically%20summarize%20results%20from%20Microsoft's%20Bing.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-satya-nadella-openai-partnership-competition-collaboration-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMicrosoft%20has%20a%20partnership%20with%20OpenAI%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20has%20invested%20billions%20of%20dollars%20in%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESearchGPT%20will%20also%20allow%20users%20to%20connect%20with%20publishers%20by%20citing%20and%20linking%20%26quot%3Bclear%2C%20in-line%2C%20named%20attribution%20and%20links%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20announcement%20said.%20The%20feature%20will%20help%20users%20figure%20out%20where%20information%20is%20coming%20from%20and%20will%20allow%20them%20to%20engage%20with%20more%20results%20in%20a%20side%20bar%20with%20links.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20big%20money%20to%20be%20had%20in%20search%2C%20and%20Google%20is%20the%20undisputed%20leader.%20The%20lion's%20share%20of%20Google's%20revenue%20comes%20from%20its%20search%20business%20%E2%80%94%20%24175%20billion%20in%20revenue%20came%20from%20Google%20search%20and%20related%20ads%20last%20year%2C%20up%20from%20%24162.45%20billion%20in%202022%2C%20its%20annual%20report%20shows.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EIt%20also%20has%20about%20a%2090%25%20share%20of%20the%20search%20market%2C%20the%20Department%20of%20Justice%20said%20recently%20in%20the%20closing%20arguments%20of%20its%20antitrust%20case%20against%20Google.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20comparison%2C%20Microsoft's%20Bing%20has%20a%205.5%25%20share%20of%20the%20search%20market%2C%20the%20DOJ%20said.%20But%20Microsoft%20seems%20serious%20about%20its%20AI%20search%20ambitions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMicrosoft%20introduced%20its%20AI-powered%20Bing%20last%20February.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20CEO%20Satya%20Nadella%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fblogs.microsoft.com%2Fblog%2F2023%2F02%2F07%2Freinventing-search-with-a-new-ai-powered-microsoft-bing-and-edge-your-copilot-for-the-web%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%26quot%3BAI%20will%20fundamentally%20change%20every%20software%20category%2C%20starting%20with%20the%20largest%20category%20of%20all%20%E2%80%94%20search.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI's%20announcement%20comes%20after%20The%20Information%20in%20February%20that%20the%20company%20had%20been%20quietly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-google-online-search-product-chatgpt-microso