show%2F112021676.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fa-year-jail-sentence-should-be-given-to-anyone-who-desecrates-american-flag-trump%2Famp_articleshow%2F112021676.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Centre%20Criticises%20Kerala%20For%20Appointing%20Official%20For%20%26quot%3BExternal%20Cooperation%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EState%20governments%20should%20not%20intrude%20into%20matters%20beyond%20their%20constitutional%20jurisdiction%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20(MEA)%20said%20on%20Thursday%20criticising%20the%20Kerala%20government%20for%20appointing%20a%20secretary%20for%20%26quot%3Bexternal%20cooperation%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECiting%20provisions%20in%20the%20Constitution%2C%20MEA%20spokesperson%20Randhir%20Jaiswal%20said%20that%20matters%20relating%20to%20foreign%20affairs%20are%20the%20%26quot%3Bsole%20prerogative%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20central%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20July%2015%2C%20the%20Kerala%20government%20issued%20an%20order%20giving%20K%20Vasuki%2C%20secretary%20in%20the%20labour%20and%20skills%20department%2C%20the%20additional%20charge%20of%20%26quot%3Bthe%20matters%20connected%20with%20external%20cooperation%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Constitution%20of%20India%20under%20the%20seventh%20schedule%2C%20list%201%20(or%20the)%20Union%20list%2C%20item%2010%2C%20clearly%20specifies%20that%20foreign%20affairs%20and%20all%20matters%20which%20bring%20the%20Union%20into%20relation%20with%20any%20foreign%20country%2C%20are%20the%20sole%20prerogative%20of%20the%20Union%20Government%2C%26quot%3B%20Jaiswal%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20not%20a%20concurrent%20subject%20and%20definitely%20not%20a%20state%20subject.%20Our%20position%20is%20that%20state%20governments%20should%20not%20intrude%20into%20matters%20that%20are%20beyond%20their%20constitutional%20jurisdiction%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20BJP%20parliamentarian%20P%20P%20Chaudhary%20raised%20the%20issue%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20described%20the%20Kerala%20government's%20action%20as%20%26quot%3Bunconstitutional%26quot%3B%20and%20an%20%26quot%3Bencroachment%26quot%3B%20on%20the%20responsibilities%20of%20the%20Centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIs%20the%20Kerala%20government%20treating%20itself%20as%20a%20separate%20nation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20lawmaker%20said%20external%20cooperation%20meant%20dealing%20with%20various%20nations%2C%20Indian%20embassies%20and%20missions%20abroad%2C%20functions%20that%20formed%20part%20of%20the%20Union%20List%20as%20per%20the%20allocation%20of%20business%20rules.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20per%20the%20allocation%20of%20business%20rules%2C%20these%20functions%20can%20only%20be%20performed%20by%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20through%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20MP%20from%20Pali%20in%20Rajasthan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%2C%20the%20action%20on%20the%20part%20of%20Kerala%20government%20by%20issuing%20such%20an%20order%20and%20appointing%20an%20IAS%20officer%20as%20foreign%20secretary%20is%20unconstitutional%2C%20and%20it%20is%20an%20encroachment%20on%20the%20union%20list%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721928660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-03%2F8iq51ge4_pinarayi-vijayan-1200_625x300_18_March_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentre-criticises-kerala-for-appointing-official-for-external-cooperation-6188884%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22State%20governments%20should%20not%20intrude%20into%20matters%20beyond%20their%20constitutional%20jurisdiction%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20(MEA)%20said%20on%20Thursday%20criticising%20the%20Kerala%20government%20for%20appointing%20a%20secretary%20for%20%26quot%3Bexternal%20cooperation%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentre-criticises-kerala-for-appointing-official-for-external-cooperation-6188884%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentre-criticises-kerala-for-appointing-official-for-external-cooperation-6188884%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentre-criticises-kerala-for-appointing-official-for-external-cooperation-6188884%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22EQT%20Private%20Cap%20Asia%20exits%20RBL%20Bank%2C%20sells%20entire%20stake%20for%20Rs%201%2C091%20cr%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721928455000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-05%2F14%2Fthumb%2Ffeaturecrop%2F400X400%2F1715665282-6014.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Feqt-private-cap-asia-exits-rbl-bank-sells-entire-stake-for-rs-1-091-cr-124072501313_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20per%20the%20data%20available%20on%20the%20BSE%2C%20Maple%20II%20B%20V%20sold%204%2C78%2C40%2C700%20shares%2C%20amounting%20to%20a%207.89%20per%20cent%20stake%20in%20RBL%20Bank%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Feqt-private-cap-asia-exits-rbl-bank-sells-entire-stake-for-rs-1-091-cr-124072501313_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Feqt-private-cap-asia-exits-rbl-bank-sells-entire-stake-for-rs-1-091-cr-124072501313_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Feqt-private-cap-asia-exits-rbl-bank-sells-entire-stake-for-rs-1-091-cr-124072501313_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20drones%20and%20the%20battle%20for%20Ukraine%20are%20changing%20the%20future%20of%20warfare%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721927533000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2Fa454%2Flive%2Fed49c290-4aa8-11ef-8f0f-0577398c3339.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fvideos%2Fcw4y2mrp4jwo%230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Drone%20technology%20has%20made%20the%20war%20more%20immediate%20and%20more%20deadly%20%E2%80%93%20and%20opened%20up%20a%20new%20battleground.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A36%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fvideos%2Fcw4y2mrp4jwo%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Not%20For%20Pension%20Scheme%20That%20Helps%20Some%2C%20Is%20Disastrous%20For%20Rest%3A%20Top%20Official%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThis%20year's%20Union%20Budget%2C%20which%20has%20been%20at%20the%20receiving%20end%20of%20the%20opposition's%20ire%20because%20of%20the%20alleged%20preferential%20treatment%20given%20to%20certain%20states%20-%20especially%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20and%20Bihar%20-%20is%20not%20discriminatory%20and%20a%20set%20formula%20is%20in%20place%20for%20the%20devolution%20of%20taxes%2C%20Finance%20Secretary%20TV%20Somanathan%20has%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20exclusively%20to%20NDTV%20on%20Thursday%2C%20Mr%20Somanathan%20also%20said%20that%20the%20Agnipath%20scheme%20is%20just%20a%20variation%20of%20short%20service%20commissions%2C%20which%20have%20existed%20forever%2C%20and%20is%20financially%20prudent.%20As%20announced%20in%20the%20Budget%2C%20the%20new%20pension%20scheme%20will%20be%20tweaked%20to%20address%20the%20key%20issues%20raised%20by%20beneficiaries%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20the%20opposition's%20allegations%20of%20discrimination%2C%20the%20senior%20bureaucrat%20said%20he%20does%20not%20want%20to%20go%20into%20the%20political%20aspects%20of%20the%20matter%20but%20on%20the%20purely%20financial%20front%2C%20it%20was%20a%20question%20of%20following%20laid-down%20formulas.%20Disagreements%2C%20he%20said%2C%20could%20arise%20in%20central%20schemes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20the%20finance%20ministry's%20transfers%2C%20what%20are%20the%20things%20that%20we%20handle%3F%20We%20handle%20devolution%2C%20which%20is%20the%20share%20of%20taxes%2C%20and%20we%20have%20the%20finance%20commission%20grants%20-%20%C2%A0both%20of%20these%20are%20determined%20by%20the%20finance%20commission%2C%20and%20we%20don't%20deviate.%20The%20other%20new%20scheme%20that%20we%20operate%20is%20special%20assistance%20to%20states%20for%20capital%20investment%2C%20which%20is%20also%20largely%20formulaic.%20Some%20part%20of%20it%20is%20untied.%20Some%20part%20of%20it%20is%20tied%20to%20specific%20reform%20outcomes%2C%20and%20we%20have%20actually%20disbursed%20money%20to%20almost%20all%20the%20states%20under%20that%20scheme%2C%20and%20I%20have%20not%20heard%20any%20complaints%20on%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Somanathan%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20there%20has%20been%20no%20discrimination%2C%20definitely%20not%20in%20the%20allocations%20by%20the%20finance%20ministry.%20And%20I%20don't%20think%20even%20in%20the%20case%20of%20other%20ministries.%20Problems%20or%20issues%20may%20arise%20when%20something%20is%20a%20programme%20of%20the%20central%20government%2C%20where%20the%20Centre%20has%20the%20prerogative%20to%20decide%20where%20and%20how%20it%20is%20used.%20So%20that%20is%20a%20matter%20where%20the%20elected%20executive%20at%20the%20Centre%20decides%20in%20its%20domain%20and%20the%20elected%20executive%20of%20the%20state%20can%20ask%20the%20Centre%20what%20it%20wants.%20But%20final%20decisions%20remain%20with%20the%20Centre%2C%20and%20that%20is%20a%20realm%20where%20officers%20like%20me%20have%20very%20little%20to%20say%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20finance%20secretary%20insisted%20that%2C%20putting%20politics%20aside%2C%20the%20coordination%20between%20the%20Centre%20and%20all%20states%20at%20the%20administrative%20level%20is%20very%20smooth.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20continue%20to%20be%20in%20regular%20touch%20with%20the%20finance%20secretaries%20of%20the%20state%20and%20the%20chief%20secretaries.%20Our%20dialogue%20continues%20to%20be%20very%20professional.%20So%2C%20this%20country%20is%20very%20resilient.%20We%20have%20some%20very%20good%20federal%20systems.%20And%20the%20all-India%20services%20are%20an%20example%20of%20a%20federal%20system%20where%20the%20same%20set%20of%20officers%20work%20both%20in%20the%20states%20and%20at%20the%20Centre.%20So%2C%20somebody%20who%20was%20my%20colleague%20till%20yesterday%20in%20this%20ministry%20is%20now%20the%20finance%20secretary%20of%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%20We%20have%20mechanisms%20for%20dealing%20with%20these%20problems%20which%20are%20outside%20the%20realm%20of%20politics%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAgnipath%20Scheme%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Agnipath%20scheme%20has%20been%20a%20contentious%20issue%20between%20the%20Centre%20and%20the%20opposition%20and%20it%20is%20also%20believed%20to%20have%20cost%20the%20BJP%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20some%20states%2C%20especially%20those%20from%20where%20a%20large%20number%20of%20youth%20enrol%20in%20the%20armed%20forces.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Mr%20Somanathan%20was%20asked%20about%20speculation%20that%20changes%20are%20likely%20in%20the%20scheme%2C%20which%20would%20benefit%20those%20who%20join%20the%20Army%2C%20Navy%20or%20Air%20Force%20as%20Agniveers%2C%20he%20said%20he%20is%20not%20aware%20of%20any%20such%20plans.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20not%20an%20expert%20on%20Agnipath.%20You%20will%20have%20to%20ask%20the%20defence%20secretary%2C%20but%20I%20am%20not%20aware%20of%20any%20changes%20in%20the%20Agniveer%20system.%20I%20think%20it's%20a%20good%20system.%20I%20think%20a%20lot%20of%20armies%20across%20the%20world%20have%20moved%20to%20short%20service%20commissions.%20The%20word%20Agniveer%20is%20new%2C%20but%20short%20service%20commissions%20have%20existed%20for%20ages%2C%20not%20only%20in%20India%20but%20elsewhere%20as%20well.%20Short%20service%20commissions%20are%20a%20useful%20way%20of%20ensuring%20that%20you%20have%20a%20youthful%20infantry.%20This%20is%20especially%20important%20given%20the%20kind%20of%20borders%20that%20India%20has%2C%20where%20there%20is%20very%20difficult%20terrain%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20finance%20secretary%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20there%20are%20a%20number%20of%20merits%20in%20the%20scheme.%20It%20is%20also%20financially%20very%20prudent%20because%20the%20armed%20forces%20are%20still%20on%20the%20old%20pension%20scheme%2C%20which%20is%20a%20very%20expensive%20scheme%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20pointed%20out.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPension%20Tweaks%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Somanathan%2C%20who%20is%20heading%20a%20committee%20discussing%20possible%20changes%20in%20the%20new%20pension%20scheme%2C%20said%20an%20announcement%20has%20been%20made%20in%20the%20Budget%20by%20Finance%20Minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20and%20details%20are%20being%20worked%20out.%20He%20said%20that%20the%20government%20is%20committed%20to%20ensuring%20that%20the%20key%20areas%20of%20concern%20are%20addressed%20but%20emphasised%20that%20it%20does%20not%20want%20a%20system%20which%20is%20beneficial%20for%20one%20class%20of%20people%2C%20but%20%26quot%3Bdisastrous%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20rest.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20had%20four%20rounds%20of%20consultations%20with%20our%20staff%20associations%20through%20the%20National%20Council%20of%20Joint%20Consultative%20Machinery.%20We%20have%20understood%20what%20the%20core%20concerns%20are.%20One%20thing%20that%20I%20can%20say%20as%20the%20head%20of%20the%20committee%20-%20I%20can't%20speak%20for%20the%20government%20on%20this%20-%20is%20that%20a%20return%20to%20the%20old%20pension%20system%20is%20completely%20not%20feasible%20financially...%20It%20will%20be%20a%20disaster%20for%20those%20citizens%20of%20India%20who%20are%20not%20government%20servants.%20It%20may%20be%20desirable%20for%20one%20class%20of%20people%2C%20but%20it%20will%20be%20a%20disaster%20for%20the%20rest%2C%20so%20that%20is%20not%20feasible%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Somanathan%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20we%20have%20understood%20through%20these%20discussions%20what%20the%20core%20concerns%20of%20employees%20are.%20They%20would%20like%20an%20assurance%20of%20the%20amount%20of%20pension%20they%20would%20get%20and%20not%20be%20dependent%20on%20market%20fluctuations.%20Second%2C%20they%20would%20like%20some%20form%20of%20inflation%20protection%20for%20that%20pension.%20And%20the%20third%2C%20for%20those%20whose%20service%20falls%20short%20of%20the%20required%20guaranteed%20level%2C%20could%20there%20be%20a%20minimum%20pension%20for%20them%3F%20I%20think%20we%20will%20be%20able%20to%20find%20a%20way%20to%20address%20these%20concerns%20to%20a%20satisfactory%20level.%20And%20that%20is%20the%20effort%20that%20we%20are%20working%20towards%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added%2C%20stressing%20that%20the%20steps%20would%20be%20taken%20keeping%20fiscal%20prudence%20in%20mind.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndustry%20On%20Board%20With%20Internship%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20aspects%20of%20the%20internship%20programme%20announced%20by%20the%20government%20in%20the%20Budget%20as%20part%20of%20its%20employment%20generation%20push%20have%20also%20been%20criticised%20and%20sources%20clarified%20on%20Wednesday%20that%20the%20top%20500%20companies%20would%20not%20be%20forced%20to%20participate.%20The%20finance%20secretary%20told%20NDTV%20that%20the%20government%20had%20consulted%20industry%20on%20the%20broad%20contours%2C%20but%20admitted%20that%20the%20specific%20scheme%20that%20was%20announced%20had%20not%20been%20discussed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20completely%20voluntary.%20We%20had%20consulted%20trade%20and%20industry%20on%20the%20broad%20issues%20of%20skilling%20and%20they%20have%20generally%20been%20very%20forthcoming%20in%20terms%20of%20saying%20that%20this%20is%20something%20they%20would%20like%20to%20partner%20on.%20They%20have%20not%20necessarily%20been%20consulted%20on%20the%20specific%20parameters%20of%20the%20scheme%20that's%20been%20outlined%20in%20the%20budget%2C%20no.%20But%20it%20is%20not%20contrary%20to%20what%20they%20are%20capable%20of%20doing%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20scheme%20centres%20around%20the%20use%20of%20corporate%20social%20responsibility%20(CSR)%20funds%20in%20a%20focused%20manner%20for%20skilling.%20We%20are%20focusing%20on%20those%20companies%20which%20are%20part%20of%20the%20CSR%20requirement%20under%20the%20Companies%20Act.%20There%20are%20about%2020%2C000%20companies%2C%20very%20roughly%2C%20who%20spend%20approximately%2026%2C000%20crores%20on%20CSR.%20500%20companies%20would%20(account%20for)%20nearly%20two-thirds%20of%20that%20total.%20So%20this%20is%20a%20manageable%20universe%20which%20is%20easy%20to%20monitor%20and%20work%20with%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20finance%20secretary%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStating%20that%20the%20government%20will%20pay%2090%25%20of%20the%20stipend%20and%20the%20relocation%20and%20incidental%20costs%2C%20he%20said%20the%20volunteering%20companies%20would%20skill%20the%20person%20in%20a%20trade%20that%20they%20are%20engaged%20in.%20They%20could%20also%20use%20companies%20in%20their%20supply%20chain%20for%20this.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhatever%20expense%20they%20incur%20will%20be%20from%20their%20CSR%20funds.%20So%20it%20doesn't%20affect%20their%20bottom%20line%20in%20any%20respect.%20They%20do%20a%20number%20of%20other%20CSR%20activities%2C%20but%20those%20are%20usually%20in%20the%20domain%20that%20the%20government%20can%20also%20do%20-%20the%20government%20can%20also%20set%20up%20schools%20and%20build%20toilets.%20But%20the%20government%20cannot%20do%20industrial%20skilling.%20So%20this%20is%20a%20unique%20advantage%20which%20the%20private%20sector%20has%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20stressing%20that%20the%20selection%20process%20for%20such%20interns%20would%20be%20fair%20and%20transparent.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThrust%20On%20Foreign%20Direct%20Investment%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaking%20it%20clear%20that%20the%20government%20is%20welcoming%20Foreign%20Direct%20Investment%20(FDI)%20in%20%26quot%3Bevery%20way%2C%20shape%20and%20form%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20finance%20secretary%20pointed%20to%20the%20focus%20on%20plug-and-play%20infrastructure%20being%20set%20up%20in%20various%20places%20to%20ease%20the%20regulatory%20compliance%20burden%20on%20companies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20mentioned%20a%20number%20of%20things%20in%20the%20speech%20on%20plug-and-play%20infrastructure...%20100%20such%20places%20being%20chosen...%2010%20nodes%20on%20the%20industrial%20corridors.%20So%20these%20are%20all%20going%20to%20make%20it%20easier%20for%20FDI%20to%20come%20and%20set%20up%20in%20India%20without%20having%20to%20go%20through%20the%20entire%20process%20of%20getting%20regulatory%20approvals%20for%20each%20step.%20So%20a%20pre-approved%20package%20of%20land%2C%20labour%2C%20infrastructure%2C%20pollution%20clearance%2C%20electricity%2C%20roads%2C%20water%20-%20everything%20that%20you%20need%20to%20set%20up.%20an%20industry%20-%20should%20be%20ready%20when%20you%20come%20in%2C%20and%20this%20is%20the%20aim%20we%20are%20working%20on%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721927340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2F287pli1g_tv-somanathan-interview_625x300_25_July_24.