f%20how%20sometimes%20we%20forget%20to%20give%20ourselves%20time%20off%20from%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Patel%20uploaded%20a%20screenshot%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%20alongside%20a%20caption%20%26quot%3BIndian%20engineers%20are%20a%20different%20breed.%26quot%3B%20As%20per%20the%20post%2C%20Mr%20Patel%20asked%20the%20employee%20to%20take%20some%20time%20off%2C%20but%20the%20employee%20said%20that%20he%20did%20not%20need%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3Eindian%20engineers%20are%20a%20different%20breed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FfYdMundMfy%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FfYdMundMfy%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Roshan%20Patel%20(%40roshanpateI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FroshanpateI%2Fstatus%2F1816142577134907543%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJuly%2024%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CEO%20told%20the%20employee%2C%20%26quot%3BHey%20noticed%20you%20haven't%20taken%20any%20time%20off%20in%20a%20while.%20just%20checking%20in%20and%20definitely%20encourage%20you%20to%20take%20a%20break%20if%20needed!%26quot%3B%20To%20this%2C%20the%20engineer%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20dont%20need%20break%20sir.%20my%20body%20is%20a%20vessel%20for%20the%20company%20to%20find%20product%20market%20fit.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20being%20shared%2C%20the%20post%20has%20amassed%20over%20four%20million%20views%20and%2075%2C000%20likes%20on%20the%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BElon%20Musk%20searching%20for%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20user.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BThey%20really%20are%20though.%20Once%20worked%20at%20a%20consultancy%20where%20majority%20of%20my%20team%20was%20Indian.%20They%20grind%20like%20no%20other.%20Potluck%20days%20were%20on%20another%20level%20too.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20third%20user%20commented%2C%20%26quot%3Bif%20you%20haven't%20noticed%20the%20underlying%20sarcasm%20you%20haven't%20worked%20with%20indian%20engineers%20enough%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20who%20have%20built%20something%20will%20100%25%20relate%20to%20this%2C%20others%20might%20just%20call%20this%20toxic%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20user%20added%2C%20%26quot%3Bcan't%20possibly%20stress%20enough%20about%20how%20CORPORATE%20DOESNT%20OWE%20YOU%20S***%20get%20a%20life%20beyond%20your%20job%2C%20they%20only%20and%20only%20care%20about%20themselves%20and%20their%20profits%20babe%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20actually%20ptsd%20from%20working%20under%20toxic%20indian%20management%20for%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20remarked%20a%20user.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721923920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fvq5c8leg_laptop_625x300_15_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fceo-says-indian-engineers-are-a-different-breed-due-to-this-reason-internet-reacts-6188383%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Since%20being%20shared%2C%20the%20post%20has%20amassed%20over%20four%20million%20views%20and%2075%2C000%20likes%20on%20the%20platform.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fceo-says-indian-engineers-are-a-different-breed-due-to-this-reason-internet-reacts-6188383%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fceo-says-indian-engineers-are-a-different-breed-due-to-this-reason-internet-reacts-6188383%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fceo-says-indian-engineers-are-a-different-breed-due-to-this-reason-internet-reacts-6188383%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Robber%20grandpas'%3A%20Elderly%20trio%20charged%20with%20burglary%20in%20Japan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721923803000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2