arty%20to%20stand%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Pawan%20Kalyan%2C%20Human%20Resources%20Development%20Minister%20Nara%20Lokesh%20and%20several%20other%20ministers%20were%20among%20those%20who%20stood%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20women%20MLAs%20heard%20saying%20she%20had%20seven%20cases%20booked%20against%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCases%20were%20booked%20against%20all%20those%20who%20were%20fighting%20politically.%20He%20(former%20Chief%20Minister%20Jagan%20Mohan%20Reddy)%20did%20not%20want%20to%20see%20any%20of%20them%20out%20(of%20jail)%20but%20people%20sent%20all%20of%20them%20directly%20to%20the%20Assembly%2C%26quot%3B%20Naidu%20said%20in%20the%20Assembly%20while%20presenting%20a%20White%20Paper%20on%20the%20law%20and%20order%20situation%20during%20the%20YSRCP%20rule.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Naidu%20vowed%20to%20place%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20in%20the%20first%20position%20in%20the%20country%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20best%20law%20and%20order%20situation.%20He%20said%20all%20the%20politically%20motivated%20cases%20would%20be%20reviewed.%20The%20Chief%20Minister%20said%20the%20government%20was%20also%20ready%20to%20punish%20all%20those%20officials%20who%20registered%20illegal%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20except%20the%20Babli%20case%2C%20he%20never%20had%20any%20other%20case%20against%20him%20but%20after%20the%20YSRCP%20came%20to%20power%2C%2017%20cases%20were%20booked%20against%20him%20while%20seven%20cases%20were%20booked%20against%20Pawan%20Kalyan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Naidu%20mentioned%20that%20about%2060%20cases%20were%20booked%20against%20TDP%20leader%20J.%20C.%20Prabhakar%20Reddy.%20Cases%20under%20the%20SC%2FST%20Atrocities%20Act%20were%20registered%20against%20present%20Home%20Minister%20Anitha%20Vangalapudi%20and%20Speaker%20Ayyanna%20Patrudu.%20Then%20MP%20Raghurama%20Krishna%20Raju%20was%20tortured%20in%20lock-up%2C%20he%20said%20and%20alleged%20that%20then%20Chief%20Minister%20Jagan%20Mohan%20Reddy%20drew%20sadistic%20pleasure%20by%20watching%20the%20video%20of%20the%20torture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20alleged%20that%20under%20the%20YSRCP%20rule%2C%20people%20suffered%20physical%20and%20mental%20trauma.%20%26quot%3BYSRCP%20leaders%20with%20the%20police%20attacked%20the%20very%20roots%20of%20democracy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20and%20recalled%20that%20the%20Legislative%20Council%20Chairman%20was%20not%20allowed%20to%20function%20when%20a%20bill%20for%20creating%20three%20state%20capitals%20was%20tabled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Naidu%20agreed%20to%20Pawan%20Kalyan's%20suggestion%20that%20another%20session%20be%20called%20for%20a%20thorough%20discussion%20on%20law%20and%20order.%20He%20also%20advised%20NDA%20members%20not%20to%20land%20the%20government%20in%20trouble%20and%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20the%20government%20would%20punish%20anyone%20disturbing%20peace%20and%20law%20and%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Minister%20said%20law%20and%20order%20can%20be%20maintained%20when%20officials%20perform%20their%20duties%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20law.%20He%20also%20assured%20the%20house%20that%20a%20separate%20wing%20would%20be%20created%20in%20the%20police%20department%20to%20monitor%20social%20media.%20He%20warned%20that%20those%20posting%20content%20derogatory%20to%20women%20would%20not%20be%20spared.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721923260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F9k0m6l6g_chandrababu-naidu_625x300_12_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhen-80-andhra-mlas-stood-up-in-response-to-this-question-by-chandrababu-naidu-6188161%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20Assembly%20witnessed%20some%20lighter%20moments%20on%20Thursday%20as%20almost%2080%20per%20cent%20of%20