2-year-old%20finished%20fourth%20in%20the%20men's%20archery%20ranking%20round%20at%20the%20Paris%20Olympics%202024%20on%20Thursday.%20It%20was%20a%20tremendous%20effort%20from%20Dhiraj%20as%20he%20made%20a%20late%20surge%20in%20the%20rankings%20and%20guided%20India%20to%20the%20quarterfinals%20of%20the%20team%20event.%20Dhiraj%20ultimately%20ended%20with%20681%20points%20while%20his%20teammates%20-%20Tarundeep%20Rai%20and%20Pravin%20Jadhav%20-%20finished%2014th%20and%2039th%20respectively.%20Hailing%20from%C2%A0Vijayawada%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20Dhiraj's%20journey%20has%20been%20filled%20with%20tremendous%20achievements%20and%20this%20was%20another%20feat%20for%20the%20youngster%20who%20has%20done%20well%20in%20the%20past%20couple%20of%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDhiraj's%20father%20Bommadevara%20Shravan%20Kumar%20used%20to%20be%20a%20technical%20official%20of%20the%20Archery%20Association%20of%20India.%20The%20youngster%20started%20training%20at%20the%C2%A0Volga%20Archery%20Academy%20in%20Vijayawada%20in%202006%20before%20joining%20the%20Indian%20Army%20in%202021after%20training%20at%20the%20Army%20Sports%20Institute%20in%20Pune%20for%20four%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERanked%2015th%20in%20the%20world%2C%20Dhiraj%20booked%20his%20berth%20for%20the%20Paris%20Olympics%202024%20in%20Bangkok%20and%20in%20the%20build-up%20to%20the%20competition%2C%20he%20clinched%20the%20bronze%20medal%20at%20the%20World%20Cup%202024%20in%20Antalya%2C%20Turkey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDhiraj%20was%20part%20of%20the%20Indian%20men's%20team%20that%20went%20on%20to%20clinch%20the%20silver%20medal%20at%20the%20Asian%20Games%202023%20along%20with%20Atanu%20Das%20and%20Tushar%20Shelke.%20They%20ended%20up%20losing%20the%20final%20against%20Republic%20of%20Korea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBack%20in%202017%2C%20Dhiraj%20Bommadevara%20made%20his%20debut%20at%20the%20international%20level.%20However%2C%20he%20did%20wait%20a%20bit%20for%20his%20first%20success%20as%20he%20won%20the%20gold%20medal%20in%20the%202021%20World%20Archer%20Youth%20Championships.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20women's%20team%20secured%20a%20fourth-place%20finish%20in%20the%20ranking%20round%20to%20seal%20a%20spot%20in%20the%20quarterfinal%20stage%20at%20Les%20Invalides%20in%20Paris%20on%20Thursday.%20In%20the%20quarterfinals%2C%20India%20will%20face%20the%20winner%20of%20the%20last-16%20stage%20match%20between%20hosts%20France%20and%20the%20Netherlands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20individual%20round%2C%20Ankita%20Bhakat%20bagged%20the%2011th%20spot%20with%20a%20season-best%20score%20of%20666%20after%2072%20shots%2C%20including%2030%20tens%20and%209%20Xs.%20She%20picked%2054%20points%20in%20the%20final%20end.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBhajan%20Kaur%20scored%20659%20(25%2010s%20and%206%20Xs)to%20finish%2022nd%20in%20the%20standings.%C2%A0Deepika%C2%A0Kumari%2C%20who%20is%20competing%20in%20her%20fourth%20Olympics%2C%20settled%20for%2023rd%20place%20in%20the%20final%20standings%20with%20658%20points.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(With%20IANS%20inputs)%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721919840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fiptc442g_cc_625x300_25_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Folympics-2024%2Fwho-is-dhiraj-bommadevara-indian-archer-who-excelled-in-olympics-2024-6187932%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Dhiraj%20Bommadevara%20impressed%20everyone%20as%20the%2022-year-old%20finished%20fourth%20in%20the%20men's%20archery%20ranking%20round%20at%20the%20Paris%20Olympics%202024%20on%20Thursday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Folympics-2024%2Fwho-is-dhiraj-bommadevara-indian-archer-who-excelled-in-olympics-2024-6187932%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Folympics-2024%2Fwho-is-dhiraj-bommadevara-indian-archer-who-excelled-in-olympics-2024-6187932%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsport