s-in-india-posts-volume-growth-in-june-qtr-124072501201_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Funilever-consolidates-share-gains-in-india-posts-volume-growth-in-june-qtr-124072501201_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Funilever-consolidates-share-gains-in-india-posts-volume-growth-in-june-qtr-124072501201_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22China%20Man%20With%20Cough%20For%202%20Years%20Discovers%20It%20Was%20Caused%20By%20Chilli%20Pepper%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20man%20in%20China%2C%20whose%20cough%20had%20persisted%20for%20over%20two%20years%2C%20breathed%20a%20sigh%20of%20relief%20after%20learning%20that%20the%20reason%20was%20a%20piece%20of%20chilli%20pepper%20stuck%20in%20his%20lung%2C%20rather%20than%20cancer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2054-year-old%20man%20is%20from%20the%20eastern%20Chinese%20province%20of%20Zhejiang%20and%20is%20only%20known%20by%20his%20last%20name%2C%20Xu.%20According%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fnews%2Fpeople-culture%2Ftrending-china%2Farticle%2F3271533%2Fspice-life-china-cancer-man-relieved-find-chilli-hotpot-caused-2-year-cough%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESouth%20China%20Morning%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%20had%20been%20treating%20his%20cough%20on%20his%20own%20with%20over-the-counter%20medications%20but%20had%20not%20noticed%20any%20difference.%20He%20ultimately%20made%20the%20decision%20to%20get%20checked%20out%20at%20Zhejiang%20Hospital's%20Thoracic%20Surgery%20Department%20in%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20one-centimetre-long%20tumour%20inside%20his%20right%20lung%20was%20discovered%20by%20a%20CT%20scan%2C%20raising%20the%20possibility%20that%20he%20was%20suffering%20from%20pneumonia%20or%20a%20cancerous%20tumour.%20Further%2C%20the%20man's%20concern%20about%20lung%20cancer%20grew%20after%20advanced%20tests%20showed%20swollen%20mediastinal%20lymph%20nodes%2C%20which%20are%20located%20in%20the%20chest's%20middle%20region%20between%20the%20lungs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20July%203%2C%20Mr.%20Xu%20had%20a%20thoracoscopy%20to%20remove%20a%20portion%20of%20his%20lung%20tissue%20so%20that%20a%20test%20could%20be%20performed%20to%20confirm%20the%20cancer.%20However%2C%20doctors%20were%20surprised%20to%20detect%20the%20tip%20of%20a%20chilli%20pepper%2C%20a%20foreign%20object%20lodged%20in%20the%20area.%20Mr.%20Xu%20then%20recalled%20badly%20choking%20and%20coughing%20during%20a%20hotpot%20meal%20two%20years%20ago%2C%20probably%20due%20to%20inhaling%20the%20pepper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZhu%20Xinhai%2C%20Director%20of%20the%20Thoracic%20Surgery%20Department%20at%20Zhejiang%20Hospital%2C%20said%20the%20chilli%20pepper%20could%20have%20moved%20into%20his%20lung.%20The%20foreign%20object%20was%20%26quot%3Bhidden%26quot%3B%20under%20the%20tissue%2C%20making%20it%20challenging%20to%20find%20using%20standard%20inspection%20techniques%2C%20resulting%20in%20an%20enlarged%20lymph%20in%20his%20right%20lung.%20Since%20the%20pepper%20was%20in%20his%20bronchial%20tubes%20for%20a%20long%20time%2C%20it%20developed%20a%20lung%20infection%20that%20led%20to%20a%20cough%20for%20over%20two%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721918940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2F92sddc68_chilli-pepper_625x300_25_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fchina-man-with-cough-for-over-2-years-discovers-it-was-caused-by-chilli-pepper-6187802%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20one-centimetre-long%20tumour%20inside%20his%20right%20lung%20was%20discovered%20by%20a%20CT%20scan%2C%20raising%20the%20possibility%20that%20he%20was%20suffering%20from%20pneumonia%20or%20a%20cancerous%20tumour.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fchina-man-with-cough-for-over-2-years-discovers-it-was-caused-by-chi