-bomb-attack-investigated-in-moscow-amid-conflicting-reports-military-official-was-target-13184459%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fcar-bomb-attack-investigated-in-moscow-amid-conflicting-reports-military-official-was-target-13184459%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Still%20Wasting%20AC%20Water%3F%20This%20Housing%20Society%20Saves%205000%20Litres%2FDay%20With%20a%20Brilliant%20Idea%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EEvery%20drop%20of%20water%20counts.%20This%20should%20be%20a%20mantra%20for%20everyone%20as%20the%20world%20faces%20a%20severe%20water%20shortage.%20Do%20you%20know%20how%20much%20water%20is%20used%20every%20time%20you%20flush%3F%20In%20older%20toilets%20installed%20in%20India%2C%20almost%20five%20to%20ten%20litres%20of%20water%20is%20used%20per%20flush.%20For%20a%20family%20of%20four%20using%20the%20toilet%20at%20least%20three%20times%20a%20day%20each%2C%20that%E2%80%99s%20a%20staggering%203%2C600%20litres%20of%20water%20per%20month!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20newer%20toilets%20come%20with%20low%20flush%20options%2C%20what%20can%20people%20with%20older%20toilets%20do%3F%20This%20question%20troubled%20the%20residents%20and%20management%20committee%20members%20of%20Saprem%20Co-operative%20Housing%20Society%20in%20Thane%2C%20Maharashtra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThane%2C%20like%20many%20parts%20of%20the%20country%2C%20has%20been%20facing%20a%20major%20water%20crisis%20in%20recent%20years.%20With%20reservoirs%20drying%20up%2C%20the%20Brihanmumbai%20Municipal%20Corporation%20(BMC)%20announced%20a%2010%20percent%20water%20cut%20starting%20in%20June%202024%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F335435%2Fiit-guwahati-startup-quant-solar-technologies-floating-solar-plant%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econserve%20the%20available%20water%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20has%20also%20impacted%20the%20water%20supply%20to%20the%20Thane%20Municipal%20Corporation%20(TMC).%20Consequently%2C%20it%20is%20now%20up%20to%20citizens%20to%20take%20action%2C%20both%20individually%20and%20collectively%2C%20particularly%20in%20gated%20communities%20and%20housing%20societies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20relying%20solely%20on%20the%20water%20supplied%20by%20the%20TMC%20and%20purchasing%20additional%20tankers%2C%20the%20residents%20of%20Saprem%20CHS%20decided%20to%20become%20self-sufficient%20in%20their%20water%20needs.%20How%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERead%20on%20to%20find%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20panacea%20for%20water%20woes%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBuilt%20in%201997%2C%20the%20society%20has%20two%20wings%20and%2064%20flats%20in%20total.%20Over%20the%20past%20decade%2C%20residents%20grappled%20with%20major%20water%20shortages.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20several%20days%20when%20we%20had%20water%20supply%20only%20for%20an%20hour%20or%20so.%20We%20also%20had%20to%20call%20for%20a%20water%20tanker%20from%20outside%2C%20paying%20thousands%20of%20rupees%20every%20day.%20It%20was%20a%20very%20difficult%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20Avinash%20Shaligram%2C%20secretary%2C%20Saprem%20CHS%2C%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20problem%20was%20exacerbated%20in%20households%20where%20everyone%20would%20go%20to%20work%20or%20school%20and%20return%20to%20no%20water.%20After%20enduring%20this%20ordeal%20for%20months%2C%20the%20residents%20began%20brainstorming%20and%20coming%20up%20with%20different%20solutions.%20One%20thing%20was%20clear%20%E2%80%94%20they%20wanted%20to%20save%20water%20in%20any%20way%20they%20could.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20society%20has%20a%20water%20tank%20with%20a%20capacity%20of%2020%2C000%20litres.%20As%20they%20started%20breaking%20down%20the%20basics%20of%20water%20usage%20in%20their%20households%2C%20one%20number%20stood%20out%20%E2%80%94%20the%20amount%20of%20water%20used%20in%20the%20toilets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsaprem2-1721819754.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20rooftop%20rainwater%20harvesting%20system%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsaprem2-1721819754.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsaprem2-1721819754-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsaprem2-1721819754-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsaprem2-1721819754-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsaprem2-1721819754-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-358280%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20rooftop%20rainwater%20harvesting%20system%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20found%20that%20every%20time%20we%20flush%20the%20toilet%2C%20it%20uses%20five%20litres%20of%20water.%20In%20a%20household%20of%20four%20members%20who%20each%20use%20the%20washroom%20four%20times%20a%20day%2C%20it%20amounts%20to%2080%20litres%20of%20water%20per%20day.%20For%20the%20entire%20society%2C%20that%20was%20a%20whopping%205%2C120%20litres%20of%20water%20per%20day%2C%20more%20than%201%2F4th%20of%20the%20tank%E2%80%99s%20capacity%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Shaligram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20wondered%20how%20to%20prevent%20this%20natural%20resource%20from%20being%20%E2%80%98flushed%E2%80%99%20down!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20find%20an%20alternative%20water%20source%2C%20they%20conducted%20a%20geological%20survey%20and%20dug%20a%20borewell.%20They%20struck%20water%20350%20feet%20below%20the%20surface%20and%20began%20using%20this%20water%20for%20their%20toilets.%20This%20immediately%20solved%20their%20water%20woes%2C%20providing%20a%2024-hour%20water%20supply!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20stopping%20there%2C%20the%20residents%20sought%20a%20way%20to%20recharge%20the%20groundwater.%20To%20this%20end%2C%20they%20built%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F290271%2Fmumbai-rain-man-makes-rainwater-harvesting-system-using-low-cost-innovation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erainwater%20harvesting%20system%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20rainwater%20that%20was%20being%20collected%20on%20the%20terrace%20was%20going%20to%20waste%2C%20in%20a%20drain.%20We%20wanted%20a%20system%20that%20would%20collect%20this%20water%20and%20divert%20it%20into%20the%20borewell%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Arun%20Deshmukh%2C%20management%20committee%20member%2C%20Saprem%20CHS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20it%20works%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECorrugated%20sheets%20have%20been%20installed%20on%20the%20rooftop%20with%20bars%20on%20the%20side.%20Eight%20pipes%20have%20been%20fixed%20across%20the%20length%20of%20the%20rooftop%20to%20collect%20rainwater.%20These%20pipes%20are%20connected%20to%20pipes%20on%20the%20ground%20that%20channel%20the%20water%20to%20the%20borewell.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInstalled%20almost%20three%20years%20ago%2C%20this%20system%20has%20made%20the%20residents%20self-sufficient%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F289205%2Frainwater-harvesting-system-in-tamil-nadu-helps-village-during-cyclone%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprevents%20rainwater%20from%20going%20to%20waste%3C%2Fa%3E.%20They%20have%20been%20using%20this%20water%20for%20their%20toilet%20needs%20and%20are%20now%20exploring%20ways%20to%20use%20it%20for%20other%20purposes.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20the%20water%20tested%20but%20it%20was%20unfit%20for%20other%20use.%20We%20are%20getting%20it%20tested%20again%20now%20to%20see%20if%20it%20can%20at%20least%20be%20used%20for%20washing%20clothes%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Shaligram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESaving%20AC%20Water%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20this%20solution%20produced%20phenomenal%20results%2C%20the%20eager%20residents%20looked%20for%20further%20ways%20to%20save%20water.%20Another%20significant%20source%20of%20water%20wastage%20was%20the%20water%20from%20air%20conditioners%20(ACs).%20Almost%20every%20house%20in%20the%20society%20has%20an%20AC%2C%20says%20Deshmukh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FInfographic-website-25-1721828440.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FInfographic-website-25-1721828440.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FInfographic-website-25-1721828440-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FInfographic-website-25-1721828440-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FInfographic-website-25-1721828440-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FInfographic-website-25-1721828440-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-358388%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20summers%2C%20these%20ACs%20run%20all%20night%20and%20for%20long%20hours%20during%20the%20day%2C%20especially%20on%20weekends%20and%20in%20work-from-home%20situations.%20Generally%2C%20a%20one-tonne%20air%20conditioner%20produces%2010%20litres%20of%20water%20if%20used%20for%20eight%20hours%20%E2%80%94%20with%20this%20amount%20increasing%20based%20on%20the%20size%20of%20the%20AC.%20To%20prevent%20this%20condensate%20(a%20liquid%20obtained%20by%20condensation%20of%20a%20gas%20or%20vapour)%20from%20going%20to%20waste%2C%20Saprem%20CHS%20members%20devised%20a%20method%20to%20save%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20long%20pipe%20runs%20down%20the%20building%2C%20with%20individual%20connections%20to%20each%20house%20to%20collect%20the%20condensate%20from%20their%20air%20conditioners.%20This%20water%20is%20funnelled%20into%20a%20wide%20pipe%20at%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20building%2C%20which%20is%20fitted%20with%20a%20tap%20for%20easy%20access.%20This%20pipe%20can%20hold%20up%20to%2015%20litres%20of%20water.%20This%20water%20is%20used%20to%20water%20the%20plants%20and%20wash%20vehicles%20in%20the%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsaprem-1721820003.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22This%20pipe%20collects%20AC%20condensate%20water%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsaprem-1721820003.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsaprem-1721820003-225x300.jpeg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsaprem-1721820003-500x667.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsaprem-1721820003-768x1024.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsaprem-1721820003-1152x1536.jpeg%201152w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsaprem-1721820003-640x853.jpeg%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsaprem-1721820003-150x200.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-358288%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThis%20pipe%20collects%20AC%20condensate%20water%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%2025%20cars%20and%2080%20two-wheelers.%20We%20are%20able%20to%20use%20this%20water%20to%20clean%20them%2C%20effectively%20reusing%20the%20water.%20In%20summer%20months%2C%20we%20also%20use%20it%20to%20water%20the%20plants%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Deshmukh.%20Even%20if%20we%20consider%20that%20it%20takes%20about%2010%20litres%20of%20water%20to%20wash%20a%20car%20and%20five%20litres%20to%20wash%20a%20two-wheeler%2C%20this%20system%20saves%20over%2019%2C000%20litres%20of%20water%20per%20month!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20society%20members%20are%20now%20exploring%20ways%20to%20become%20completely%20self-sufficient%20for%20their%20water%20needs.%20Shaligram%20mentions%20that%20they%20are%20happy%20to%20guide%20other%20societies%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F354201%2Fhow-to-set-up-start-rainwater-harvesting-affordable-system-diy-steps-watch-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eimplementing%20similar%20systems%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20rainwater%20harvesting%20system%20and%20the%20AC%20condensate%20pipes%20each%20currently%20cost%20Rs%201%20lakh%20to%20install.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWater%20is%20a%20finite%20resource.%20We%20need%20to%20save%20it%20in%20whatever%20way%20possible%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESources%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fsmaller-toilet-tanks-could-save-10-of-water%2Farticleshow%2F46843707.cms%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Smaller%20toilet%20tanks%20could%20save%2010%20%25%20of%20water%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%20Published%20On%208%20April%2C%202015%20Courtesy%20Times%20Of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2F