0x82.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-357965%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22592%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EMany%20companies%20hesitate%20to%20hire%20people%20with%20dwarfism.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20she%20has%20been%20striving%20to%20help%20people%20with%20dwarfism%20get%20employed%2C%20avail%20medical%20benefits%2C%20and%20even%20help%20them%20with%20marriage%20prospects.%20%E2%80%9CFor%20people%20with%20dwarfism%2C%20life%20is%20tough%20in%20every%20aspect%2C%20and%20I%20want%20to%20make%20it%20as%20comfortable%20for%20them%20as%20I%20can%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20sat%20down%20with%20her%20to%20understand%20her%20story%20and%20mission%20and%20what%20she%20hopes%20to%20achieve%20with%20her%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F317421%2Fhow-to-build-inclusive-workplace-navigate-blood-disorders-thalassemia-with-employers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ededicated%20job%20fairs%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20targeted%20opportunities%20help%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20biggest%20hindrances%20people%20with%20dwarfism%20face%20is%20in%20getting%20jobs.%20Many%20companies%20hesitate%20to%20hire%20people%20with%20dwarfism%2C%20worrying%20they%20might%20not%20blend%20well%20with%20other%20employees%20or%20fit%20within%20the%20company%E2%80%99s%20infrastructural%20setup%2C%20explains%20Disha%20from%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F327878%2Fsejal-shah-mariposa-foundation-shares-lessons-for-raising-a-child-with-disability%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eher%20personal%20experience.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20May%20this%20year%2C%20at%20The%20Club%20Juhu%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20The%20Little%20People%20of%20India%2C%20along%20with%20Vividhataa%2C%20an%20organisation%20focused%20on%20sensitising%20companies%20and%20helping%20them%20fulfil%20their%20diversity%20hiring%20requirements%2C%20conducted%20a%20%E2%80%98Diversity%20Job%20Fair%E2%80%99%20in%20Mumbai.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20had%20diverse%20candidates%20ranging%20from%20LGBTQIA%2B%20individuals%2C%20women%20with%20career%20breaks%2C%20army%20veterans%2C%20acid%20attack%20survivors%2C%20and%20people%20from%20other%20socio-economic%20minority%20groups%20participating%20in%20it%2C%20and%20saw%20almost%20500%20people%20get%20interviewed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20want%20to%20change%20diversity%20ratios%20in%20organisations%20by%20initiating%20conversations%20and%20influencing%20decisions%20by%20showcasing%20that%20hiring%20based%20on%20DEI%20(Diversity%2C%20Equity%20and%20Inclusion)%20is%20the%20way%20forward%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ratnaprabha%20Sable%2C%20the%20founder%20and%20managing%20director%20of%20Vividhataa.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20open-to-all%20DEI%20seminar%2Fconference%20was%20attended%20by%20corporate%20delegates%20along%20with%20students%2C%20researchers%2C%20experts%2C%20DE%26amp%3BI%20advocates%2C%20and%20similar%20activists%20from%20all%20over%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMultiple%20panel%20discussions%2C%20fireside%20chats%2C%20and%20interactive%20workshops%20such%20as%20one-on-one%20sign%20language%20were%20held%20at%20the%20event.%20With%20a%20focus%20on%20promoting%20empathy%20and%20understanding%2C%20Vividhataa%20plans%20to%20make%20DEI%20a%20top%20priority%20for%20Indian%20organisations%20and%20global%20MNCs%20across%20India%20through%20its%20initiative.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20hit%20in%202020%20and%20traditional%20job%20fairs%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20take%20place%20due%20to%20the%20lockdown%2C%20Vividhataa%20filled%20the%20gap%20by%20launching%20%E2%80%9CIndia%E2%80%99s%201st%20Virtual%20Diversity%20Job%20Fair%202020%E2%80%9D%20to%20support%20minority%20candidates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20job%20fair%20saw%20lots%20of%20diverse%20candidates%20submitting%20their%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9s%20to%20potential%20employers%20and%20becoming%20a%20beacon%20of%20hope%20in%20an%20otherwise%20challenging%20job%20market.%20Some%20celebrated%20promising%20job%20offers%2C%20while%20others%20prepared%20for%20successive%20rounds%20of%20interviews.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTwo%20people%20with%20dwarfism%20got%20employed%20with%20Amazon%20through%20the%20fair.%20Since%20they%20were%20working%20from%20places%20where%20Amazon%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20offices%2C%20they%20were%20given%20WFH%20opportunities.%20A%20laptop%2C%20a%20table%2C%20and%20every%20other%20work%20equipment%20that%20they%20might%20need%20were%20also%20provided%20by%20the%20company%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBecause%20the%20word%20of%20the%20job%20fair%20had%20spread%20around%2C%20organisations%20which%20previously%20were%20not%20big%20on%20hiring%20candidates%20with%20disabilities%20had%20shown%20up%20as%20well.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20long-term%20impact%20of%20equal%20opportunities%20on%20the%20community%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDisha%20says%20that%20to%20her%20knowledge%2C%20there%20are%20two%20more%20organisations%20that%20work%20for%20people%20with%20dwarfism%20in%20southern%20India%2C%20but%20are%20only%20restricted%20to%20a%20few%20states.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20that%20The%20Little%20People%20of%20India%20is%20the%20only%20pan-India%20organisation%20working%20for%20the%20community%2C%20and%20that%20Disha%20is%20an%20internationally-acclaimed%20para%20athlete%2C%20her%20organisation%20came%20into%20the%20limelight%20in%20the%20last%20few%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Im